=== DESIGN TOKEN CONTRACT ===
NO hardcoded hex/rgba values in CSS. Only use:
- DesignTokens.colors.xxx — all colors
- DesignTokens.typography.xxx — all fonts
- DesignTokens.spacing.xxx — all padding/margin/gap
- DesignTokens.effects.xxx — all shadows/blur/glow
- DesignTokens.gradients.xxx — all gradients
- DesignTokens.animation.xxx — all transitions
- DesignTokens.borders.xxx — all borders
- DesignTokens.buttons.xxx — all button dimensions
- DesignTokens.inputs.xxx — all input fields

=== VISUAL VERIFICATION ===
After EACH page: npx playwright test — visual regression
diff < 2% → pass
diff >= 2% → fix Token values, NOT component CSS

=== GIT COMMIT RULE ===
One commit per page. Format: "feat: [PageName] full implementation"

