Task 1/5: Swap Page (src/app/swap/page.tsx)

LAYOUT INTENT:
- Center column: Swap form
- Right sidebar: Price chart (DexScreener embed)
- Left sidebar: Token info + recent trades

FUNCTIONAL SPEC:
1. Token Select: dropdown with search. Tokens: ION (0xe1ab61f7b093435204df32f5b3a405de55445ea8), WBNB (0xbb4CdB9CBd36B01bD1cBaEBF2De08d9173bc095c), USDT (0x55d398326f99059fF775485246999027B3197955)
2. Amount Input: text field with "MAX" button that reads wallet balance
3. Quote Display: show rate + price impact + min received (slippage 0.5%)
4. Swap Button: calls PancakeSwap V3 router (0x13f4EA83D0bd40E75C8222255bc855a974568Dd4) exactInputSingle
5. Read real token price from PancakeSwap V3 pool getReserves() → convert to human readable
6. Use NeonCard component for the swap card

TYPES:
```typescript
interface Token {
  symbol: string; address: `0x${string}`; decimals: number; logoURI: string;
}
interface SwapState {
  fromToken: Token; toToken: Token; amount: string; quote: string | null;
}
```

