Task 2/5: Pool Page (src/app/pool/page.tsx)

LAYOUT INTENT:
- Center column: Pool list (top half) + Add/Remove liquidity (bottom half)
- Right sidebar: Pool stats (TVL, Volume, Fees)
- Left sidebar: My positions

FUNCTIONAL SPEC:
1. Pool List: table with columns [Pair, TVL, APR, 24h Volume, My Liquidity]
2. Source data from PancakeSwap V3 subgraph or on-chain pool reads
3. "Add Liquidity" button opens modal/form: select two tokens + amounts → approve → addLiquidity on PancakeSwap V3 nonfungiblePositionManager (0x46A15B0b27311cedF172AB29E4f4766fbE7F4364)
4. "Remove Liquidity" button: show position NFT → decreaseLiquidity → collectFees
5. Use PoolCard component from src/components/DEX/PoolCard.tsx
6. Format TVL/Volume with Intl.NumberFormat (compact notation)

TYPES:
```typescript
interface Pool {
  pair: string; token0: Token; token1: Token; tvl: number; apr: number; volume24h: number;
}
interface Position {
  pool: Pool; liquidity: string; token0Amount: string; token1Amount: string;
}
```

