Task 3/5: Stake Page (src/app/stake/page.tsx)

LAYOUT INTENT:
- Center column: Stake form + rewards display
- Right sidebar: APR calculator + stats
- Left sidebar: Stake history

FUNCTIONAL SPEC:
1. Stake Form: amount input + duration selector (Flexible 8% | 7-day 10% | 30-day 12% | 90-day 15% | 180-day 20% | 365-day 30%)
2. "Stake" button: approve ION → stake on FeeDistributor contract
3. Unstake form: shows staked amount + accrued rewards + early exit penalty
4. Rewards display: total earned + claimable now + projected APR
5. Use StakePanel component from src/components/DEX/StakePanel.tsx
6. Read real ION balance and staking data from BSC chain

TYPES:
```typescript
interface StakePosition {
  amount: string; duration: number; apr: number; rewards: string; lockEnd: number;
}
```

============================================================

Task 4/5: Bridge Page (src/app/bridge/page.tsx)

LAYOUT INTENT:
- Center column: Bridge form (source → destination)
- Right sidebar: Transaction history
- Left sidebar: Bridge stats + fees

FUNCTIONAL SPEC:
1. Chain Selector: BSC ↔ ION (icons for each chain)
2. Token Selector: ION or wrapped ION (wION)
3. Amount Input + estimated arrival time
4. Bridge flow:
   a. Lock tokens on source chain (BSC bridge contract)
   b. Show confirmation + tx hash
   c. Show status: Locking → Confirming → Minting → Complete
5. Read real bridge contract: BSC side 0x... (from ion-dex-nuke contracts)
6. Fee display: 0.1% bridge fee

TYPES:
```typescript
interface BridgeState {
  fromChain: 'BSC' | 'ION'; toChain: 'BSC' | 'ION'; token: Token; amount: string; status: BridgeStatus;
}
type BridgeStatus = 'idle' | 'approving' | 'locking' | 'confirming' | 'minting' | 'complete' | 'failed';
```

