Task 5/5: Home/Dashboard (src/app/page.tsx)

LAYOUT INTENT:
- Center column: ION price chart (full width)
- Below chart: Quick action cards (4 cards in 2x2 grid)
- Right sidebar: Market stats (TVL, Volume, Market Cap)
- Left sidebar: Portfolio summary

FUNCTIONAL SPEC:
1. Price Chart: fetch ION/USD from DexScreener API (https://api.dexscreener.com/latest/dex/tokens/0xe1ab61f7b093435204df32f5b3a405de55445ea8) → render candlestick/line chart with Recharts
2. Quick Action Cards: 4 cards — "Swap", "Pool", "Stake", "Bridge" → each links to respective page
3. TVL Display: sum of all PancakeSwap pool TVL → formatted number
4. 24h Volume + Price Change (% green/red)
5. Market Cap from DexScreener data
6. Use glassmorphism cards with neon glow effects from DesignTokens
7. Auto-refresh price every 30s

TYPES:
```typescript
interface MarketData {
  price: number; priceChange24h: number; volume24h: number; tvl: number; marketCap: number;
}
```

